uesting device executes a particular front-end application, and wherein the obtained medical information is aggregated by the particular front-end application for presentation. 85. The system of claim 77, wherein obtaining the at least a portion of the responsive medical information comprises: establishing connection between the at least one network location and the requesting device; and routing, via the application-layer protocol, the at least one portion of the responsive medical information from the at least one network location to the requesting device.
